Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪发光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦诶 你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以去那边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生最近掉毛很严重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛会黏到衣服上的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啊 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌我麻烦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.55,0:00:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你稍微出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.53,0:02:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看看 正合身！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那是因为按你的尺寸做的 自然合身啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 挺适合你的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那方面 不是那方面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来… 像普通的… 女孩子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 看起来跟外面的小姑娘一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真喜欢你～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:02:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:02:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢你了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 黏到毛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想怎样啊 你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校哦 学校！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会交到朋友的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驴唇不对马嘴啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“对啦 名乃”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“放学回去时要不要去吃冰淇淋？”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“啊 诶 去啊 去啊”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“那之后要去唱卡拉OK么？”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“诶？ 诶…”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“但是 我…”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“从来没去过！”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“我会教给你哒～”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“大家一起去嘛～”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“啊… 好… 好的”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}“那么…”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之类的对话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.47,0:03:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊 博士！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看看 博士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样啊？ 适合我么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！好漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件睡衣 也很适合博士哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 超漂亮的～！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是跟平时一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:03:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本～～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本也超帅的～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\}你也来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手帕没问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生证没问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教科书没问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笔记本没问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铅笔盒没问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动铅笔没问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动铅笔芯没问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！没有落下东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗噗～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有落下的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？诶 什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了的话…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SNICKERS！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士～！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨房里准备好早饭和午饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请记得吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 洗好的衣服 等我回来了再拿进来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都不用做就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 学校什么时间结束啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三点半左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来的时候还要买晚饭的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到家大概五点钟吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前没说过的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五点 那都晚上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:05:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对… 但是这是学校嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我走…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不想让你去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 刚才不还说可以去的嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}不可以 名乃 不可以去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样… 都要迟到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把包还给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}滚啊滚×N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦诶 小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那么无理取闹！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 要不这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚饭做博士最喜欢的蛋包饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上回来的时候给你买鲨鱼蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶… 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再加上草莓果汁！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚啊滚×N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥川奖也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可办不到啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HDECDA2&\pos(598,107)}鸡蛋豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一时都不知道该怎么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:06:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸亏博士总算是让步了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来我也能迈出做普通人的第一步…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘得干干净净啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背上的发条…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅气的东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～的 大干一场吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！ 干劲满满的前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想了好久… 也想不出答案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果就来到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 现在给大家介绍转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东云同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果… 果然大家都很在意发条…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东云同学 请自己写下名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发条 非常显眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做点什么蒙混过去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我… 我叫东云名乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个听我说啊 那个… 这个发条啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 那个… 实际上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在来的途中被插上去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷场啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 哎呀 那个听我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就是 其实吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是骗你们的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在解释些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃啊 怎么办啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 就是说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是像拇指是USB之类的 那种机器人似的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:03.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,520)\pos(800,360)}占\N卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希～望明天～是个好～天气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 关口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要光在看书 一起玩吧～
